title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Add a table that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row
2. Preview the attached report
3. Attempt to export the data from the table containing the highlight/map
SR:
1. Open the report
2. Go to the table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row
3. Try to export the data
